  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales and Marketing Executive (Copywriting)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is one of the local leading Herbal & Wellness Beverage Companies. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Marketing & Digital Executive to be part of their Marketing team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the North – easily accessible.</strong><br /><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities of Marketing & Digital Executive</strong></p><ul><li>Manage and enhance the company’s digital presence across social media, website, and email channels.</li><li>Create and publish engaging content to strengthen brand awareness and audience engagement.</li><li>Support customer engagement, CRM activities, and lead management.</li><li>Execute online and offline marketing campaigns, including events and partnerships.</li><li>Support lead generation, sales funnel optimisation, and revenue growth initiatives.</li><li>Track marketing performance and prepare reports with insights and recommendations.</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams and external partners to deliver marketing initiatives.</li><li>Leverage digital and AI tools to improve campaign effectiveness and efficiency.</li><li>Support e-commerce and growth marketing initiatives, including customer acquisition and retention.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of experience in marketing related fields.</li><li>Diploma or Degree in Marketing related disciplines.</li><li>Strong copywriting and communication skills in English</li><li>Proficient in Adobe Creative Suite or Canva</li><li>Experience in photography and videography</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>EA License No: 19C9682<br />EA Personnel No: R2198636<br />EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</p>",
